  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The research proposes to use an innovative solution to shape brain circuits that support
      executive function and emotion reactivity -using targeted neurobehavioral intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Participants will be recruited locally in the San Francisco Bay area with certain symptoms of
      anxiety and depression. They will complete a clinical assessment and then take part in a
      cognitive-emotion training delivered online.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
