  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of depression on the SCID, a total Ham-D≥16 and Ham-D anxiety/somatization
             subscale ≥ 7.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Current medication for psychiatric disorders

          -  Pregnant females

          -  Head trauma or injury that resulted in loss of consciousness

          -  MRI contraindication
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
